HEADWORD: Pullman car
<hw>Pull"man car`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Named after Mr.
<ets>Pullman</ets>, who introduced them.]</ety> <def>A kind of sleeping
car; also, a palace car; -- often shortened to
<altname>Pullman</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

